Sure! Here's an example of how you can count the number of times a specific value appears in an array using PHP:

```php
<?php
// Sample array
$array = [1, 2, 3, 3, 4, 4, 4, 5];

// Value to count
$value = 4;

// Count the occurrences of the value
$count = 0;
foreach ($array as $item) {
    if ($item == $value) {
        $count++;
    }
}

// Output the result
echo "The value $value appears $count times in the array.";
?>
```

This code will output:

```
The value 4 appears 3 times in the array.
